**NSQ-33 Review: nsqadmin/http.go — FIX FIRST**

| # | Type | Line | Severity | Description |
|---|------|------|----------|-------------|
| 1 | BUG | 133-134 | Medium | `indexHandler` ignores errors from `staticAsset` and `template.Parse`; nil `t` causes panic on `t.Execute` |
| 2 | BUG | 408-441 | **High** | `tombstoneNodeForTopicHandler` missing `isAuthorizedAdminRequest` check — all other mutating handlers have it |
| 3 | BUG | 730 | Medium | `graphiteHandler` dereferences `response[0].DataPoints[0][0]` with no bounds/nil checks — panics on empty response |
| 4 | BUG | 747 | Medium | `doConfig` ignores `net.ParseCIDR` error; nil `ipnet` causes panic on `ipnet.Contains()` at line 758 |
